{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/LibraryLogoTrimmed.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A world swallowed by an all-consuming mist. Humanity has fallen. No heroes remain. <br>Build, fight, and carve your own path through treacherous lands where the remnants of humanity and horrors beyond reason now roam. <strong>Survive\u2026 or be <i>Mistaken.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong></strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong></strong></i><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/Slay_and_loot.png?t=1739294046\" />Defeat the Mistaken, <strong>scavenge</strong> their remains, or <strong>craft</strong> your own. <strong>Weapons, armor,</strong> and gear come with <strong>randomized attributes</strong>, meaning even a simple wooden sword could become a tool of destruction in the right hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/BuildShelter.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No sanctuary remains, so make your own. <strong>Gather resources</strong>, <strong>construct a refuge</strong>, and fortify yourself against the lurking dangers. Whether a simple camp or a stronghold, your survival depends on what you build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/Collect_Cartifacts.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scattered throughout the world are <strong>Cartifacts\u2014magically infused trading cards</strong> that can be combined for devastating effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Need more firepower? Equip <strong>Smoldering Fingers</strong> to ignite your attacks. Struggling to stay alive? <strong>Embers of a Phoenix</strong> lets you heal from fire damage dealt. <strong>Experiment, stack effects, and forge a build that bends the rules in your favor.</strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3487240?t=1739294046","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739294046","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/9383535fabe72c912a7108c6e1d2a716026967cb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739294046","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/9383535fabe72c912a7108c6e1d2a716026967cb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739294046","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/LibraryLogoTrimmed.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A world swallowed by an all-consuming mist. Humanity has fallen. No heroes remain. <br>Build, fight, and carve your own path through treacherous lands where the remnants of humanity and horrors beyond reason now roam. <strong>Survive\u2026 or be <i>Mistaken.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong></strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong></strong></i><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/Slay_and_loot.png?t=1739294046\" />Defeat the Mistaken, <strong>scavenge</strong> their remains, or <strong>craft</strong> your own. <strong>Weapons, armor,</strong> and gear come with <strong>randomized attributes</strong>, meaning even a simple wooden sword could become a tool of destruction in the right hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/BuildShelter.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No sanctuary remains, so make your own. <strong>Gather resources</strong>, <strong>construct a refuge</strong>, and fortify yourself against the lurking dangers. Whether a simple camp or a stronghold, your survival depends on what you build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/extras/Collect_Cartifacts.png?t=1739294046\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scattered throughout the world are <strong>Cartifacts\u2014magically infused trading cards</strong> that can be combined for devastating effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Need more firepower? Equip <strong>Smoldering Fingers</strong> to ignite your attacks. Struggling to stay alive? <strong>Embers of a Phoenix</strong> lets you heal from fire damage dealt. <strong>Experiment, stack effects, and forge a build that bends the rules in your favor.</strong></p>","developers":["Storken"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487240/header.jpg?t=1739294046","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> macOS 10.13 High Sierra or later<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3 (or Apple M1/M2)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Integrated Intel Iris Plus Graphics 640<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 500 MB available spa